description:
Vicks nasal decongestant inhaler provides blocked nose relief anytime, anywhere.

Features:
- Provides relief from a blocked nose in seconds to make breathing feel clear and cool
- Fast and temporary relief from nasal clogging due to colds, hay fever or upper respiratory allergy
- Easily fits in small pockets
- You can be assured that wherever a cold gets you, nasal relief is just one sniff away
- For external use only

Provides relief from blocked nose in seconds to make breathing feel clear and cool

name: Vicks Nasal Decongestant Inhaler 0.5ml
